nsed milk for one of the three milks.", "pilar_favorite": true, "category": "Dessert"}, "created_time": "2025-11-29T15:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-11-29T15:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec2e6e5c9572a566a7", "table_id": "tbl84970d4163df0185", "fields": {"recipe_name": "Pozole Rojo", "source": "Tia Rosa, Eduardo", "status": "in_progress", "difficulty": "hard", "notes": "Tia Rosa thinks guajillo chiles. Eduardo says guajillo and maybe arbol. Need to confirm full chile list. Abuela's version.", "pilar_favorite": false, "category": "Soup"}, "created_time": "2025-12-13T12:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-12-17T18:35:00Z"}, {"id": "recaaa395b5d646daed7", "table_id": "tbl84970d4163df0185", "fields": {"recipe_name": "Chiles Rellenos", "source": "Tia Rosa", "status": "tested", "difficulty": "hard", "notes": "Poblanos charred and peeled. Stuffed with queso fresco. Egg batter. Tomato broth on the side. Tia Rosa says use Mexican oregano not Italian.", "pilar_favorite": true, "category": "Main Course"}, "created_time": "2025-12-01T07:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-12-01T15:41:34Z"}, {"id": "rec849d2f37b480001d5", "table_id": "tbl84970d4163df0185", "fields": {"recipe_name": "Pozole Verde", "source": "Tia Rosa", "status": "collected", "difficulty": "hard", "notes": "Tomatillos, jalape\u00f1os, pepitas, cilantro. Hominy. Slow cooked. Garnish: radish, cabbage, lime, oregano.", "pilar_favorite": false, "category": "Soup"}, "created_time": "2025-12-04T07:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-12-09T12:07:54Z"}, {"id": "recf94ba934bf78f3eb7", "table_id": "tbl84970d4163df0185", "fields": {"recipe_name": "Sopa de Fideo", "source": "Tia Rosa", "status": "finalized", "difficulty": "easy", "notes": "Toasted vermicelli, tomato, garlic, onion, chicken broth. Pilar's comfort food as a kid.", "pilar_favorite": true, "category": "Soup"}, "created_time": "2025-12-07T07:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-12-12T01:09:40Z"}, {"id": "rec43a82a6b4b478156e", "table_id": "tbl84970d4163df0185", "fields": {"recipe_name": "